These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-1::.
House: modern, art-deco, victorian, wooden
The people have 4 different jobs:  dressmaker, fisherman, photographer, paramedic
1. the paramedic is on the left of the victorian house##1
2. the modern house is on the left of the fisherman##1
3. the wooden house is in an odd position##4
4. the photographer is on the left or right of the paramedic##3
5. the modern house is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1  |   2    |   3   |    4     |
| House   | modern | art-deco | wooden | victorian |
| Job        | dressmaker | fisherman   | paramedic | photographer    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-2::.
4 different pets are kept: mouse, lizard, turtle, ferret
There are 4 different favourite beverages: mirinda, cola, iced-tea, almond-milk
1. the owner of the lizard is on the left of the owner of the ferret##1
2. the person drinking mirinda is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1
3. the person drinking iced-tea is in an odd position##4
4. the person drinking mirinda is the owner of the mouse##1
5. the person drinking cola is on the right of the person drinking iced-tea##1
6. the person drinking mirinda is the owner of the mouse##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |    3     |     4     |
| Pet   | turtle | mouse  | lizard  | ferret |
| Beverage   | almond-milk    | mirinda | iced-tea | cola    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-3::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: montecristo, bolivar, swisher, alhambra
House: modern, victorian, art-deco, cottage
1. the alhambra-smoker is on the left or right of the cottage house##3
2. the swisher-smoker is in an even position##4
3. the cottage house is on the left or right of the bolivar-smoker##3
4. the cottage house is on the right of the art-deco house##1
5. the modern house is in an odd position##4
6. the bolivar-smoker is on the right of the swisher-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3     |      4      |
| Cigar          | alhambra | swisher | bolivar    | montecristo      |
| House   | art-deco        | cottage     | modern | victorian |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-4::.
There are 4 different nationalities: spanish, nigerian, chinese, japanese
House: tower, victorian, colonial, farmhouse
1. the nigerian is between the tower house and the farmhouse house##2
2. the japanese is on the left of the spanish##1
3. the colonial house is in an odd position##4
4. the victorian house is on the left of the farmhouse house##1
5. the victorian house is on the right of the spanish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3    |    4    |
| Nationality         | japanese | spanish | nigerian | chinese |
| House   | colonial       | tower   | victorian    | farmhouse  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-5::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: swisher, old-henry, dunhill, alhambra
4 different games are played: mah-jongg, whist, backgammon, snooker
1. the dunhill-smoker is on the right of the person playing snooker##1
2. the person playing whist is the alhambra-smoker##1
3. the person playing backgammon is on the right of the swisher-smoker##1
4. the old-henry-smoker is on the far left##1
5. the dunhill-smoker is in an odd position##4
6. the person playing mah-jongg is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |   3    |     4      |
| Cigar   | old-henry  | swisher    | dunhill   | alhambra       |
| Game   | mah-jongg | snooker | backgammon | whist |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-6::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: metal, country, disco, hip-hop
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: water-polo, surfing, soccer, sailing
1. the person who's sport is surfing is in an even position##4
2. the fan of hip-hop is on the right of the person who's sport is surfing##1
3. the fan of disco is in an odd position##4
4. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the left of the fan of metal##1
5. the person who's sport is soccer is on the left or right of the person who's sport is water-polo##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |      3      |     4     |
| Music-Genre   | disco      | country | hip-hop | metal |
| Sport   | sailing | surfing     | water-polo  | soccer  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-7::.
4 different pets are kept: dog, bird, fish, mouse
There are 4 different favourite beverages: tea, sprite, cola, iced-tea
1. the person drinking iced-tea is in an odd position##4
2. the person drinking cola is on the left of the person drinking tea##1
3. the owner of the mouse is on the left of the owner of the fish##1
4. the person drinking iced-tea is the owner of the dog##1
5. the owner of the mouse is on the left or right of the person drinking tea##3
6. the person drinking sprite is on the right of the person drinking tea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |    2    |    3    |     4     |
| Pet   | dog | mouse | fish | bird    |
| Beverage     | iced-tea | cola  | tea     | sprite |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-8::.
There 4 different types of food: watermelon, eggplant, peach, corn
There are 4 different nationalities: egyptian, pakistani, malaysian, russian
1. the russian is on the left or right of the person eating eggplant##3
2. the person eating corn is in an odd position##4
3. the russian is on the left or right of the person eating corn##3
4. the person eating corn is on the right of the russian##1
5. the person eating watermelon is between the person eating corn and the person eating eggplant##2
6. the pakistani is in an odd position##4
7. the pakistani is between the person eating watermelon and the malaysian##2
8. the person eating watermelon is on the left or right of the person eating eggplant##3

.:: Answer ::.
|       |   1   |     2      |    3    |        4        |
| Food   | eggplant | watermelon      | corn | peach |
| Nationality   | egyptian  | russian | pakistani    | malaysian            |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-9::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: chaman, vegafina, bluemaster, swisher
4 different games are played: poker, snooker, scrabble, chess
1. the bluemaster-smoker is on the left or right of the chaman-smoker##3
2. the chaman-smoker is on the right of the vegafina-smoker##1
3. the person playing poker is between the person playing snooker and the bluemaster-smoker##2
4. the person playing poker is in an odd position##4
5. the bluemaster-smoker is the person playing scrabble##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1      |    2    |    3    |   4    |
| Cigar   | swisher | vegafina   | chaman | bluemaster |
| Game    | chess     | snooker | poker     | scrabble  |

