.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-10::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: cooking, photography, dancing, drawing
4 different pets are kept: fish, horse, hamster, guinea-pig
1. the person who's hobby is cooking is the owner of the guinea-pig##1
2. the owner of the fish is on the right of the person who's hobby is cooking##1
3. the owner of the guinea-pig is between the owner of the fish and the person who's hobby is dancing##2
4. the person who's hobby is cooking is in an odd position##4
5. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left or right of the owner of the fish##3
6. the person who's hobby is photography is on the left or right of the owner of the horse##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |      3      |    4     |
| Hobby      | photography       | dancing   | cooking | drawing |
| Pet   | hamster | horse | guinea-pig        | fish    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-11::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: pall-mall, swisher, old-henry, dunhill
The people have 4 different hobbies: collecting, filmmaking, camping, dunhill-polo
1. the person who's hobby is collecting is in an even position##4
2. the person who's hobby is camping is on the right of the pall-mall-smoker##1
3. the person who's hobby is camping is on the left of the person who's hobby is dunhill-polo##1
4. the person who's hobby is dunhill-polo is on the left of the old-henry-smoker##1
5. the swisher-smoker is on the left or right of the old-henry-smoker##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |    2    |     3      |    4     |
| Cigar   | pall-mall   | dunhill   | swisher      | old-henry      |
| Hobby      | filmmaking | camping | dunhill-polo | collecting |

