.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-12::.
4 different pets are kept: rat, pony, fish, frog
There are 4 different favourite beverages: coffee, cola, tea, frogade
1. the person drinking tea is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1
2. the person drinking tea is in an even position##4
3. the owner of the pony is in an even position##4
4. the owner of the rat is on the far right##1
5. the owner of the fish is between the person drinking cola and the person drinking tea##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2    |    3    |    4    |
| Pet          | frog | pony  | fish  | rat |
| Beverage   | frogade  | tea | coffee | cola   |

