.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-13::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: sunflower, balloon-flower, daffodil, marigold
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: march, april, december, january
1. the person who's birthday is in april is in an odd position##4
2. the person who's birthday is in march is on the left of the person who growsdaffodil##1
3. the person who's birthday is in april is on the left or right of the person who growssunflower##3
4. the person who growsballoon-flower is in an odd position##4
5. the person who's birthday is in april is on the far left or far right##3
6. the person who's birthday is in december is on the right of the person who growsdaffodil##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2   |   3    |     4     |
| Flower   | balloon-flower | sunflower | daffodil | marigold  |
| Birthday     | april   | march  | january  | december |

