.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-14::.
There 4 different types of food: papaya, apple, radish, corn
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: bellflower, marigold, balloon-flower, lily
1. the person who growsballoon-flower is in an odd position##4
2. the person eating papaya is in an odd position##4
3. the person eating corn is on the left of the person who growsballoon-flower##1
4. the person who growsbellflower is on the right of the person who growslily##1
5. the person eating papaya is on the left or right of the person eating apple##3
6. the person who growsbellflower is on the left or right of the person who growslily##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |   3    |      4       |
| Food   | radish | corn | papaya | apple |
| Flower           | lily     | bellflower     | balloon-flower   | marigold         |

