.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-15::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: chestnut, coral, lilac, orange
4 different games are played: go, whist, scrabble, snooker
1. the person who likes chestnut is between the person playing go and the person who likes coral##2
2. the person who likes lilac is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person who likes coral is on the left of the person playing snooker##1
4. the person who likes orange is on the left of the person who likes coral##1
5. the person playing snooker is in an odd position##4
6. the person playing scrabble is on the left of the person playing whist##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |       2       |       3       |      4       |
| Color   | orange | coral         | chestnut   | lilac |
| Game   | scrabble    | whist | snooker | go   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-16::.
4 different pets are kept: hedgehog, lizard, cat, chinchilla
4 different games are played: scrabble, chess, snooker, whist
1. the person playing whist is the owner of the cat##1
2. the person playing snooker is the owner of the hedgehog##1
3. the person playing chess is the owner of the chinchilla##1
4. the owner of the cat is on the left or right of the owner of the chinchilla##3
5. the owner of the hedgehog is in an even position##4
6. the owner of the cat is on the right of the person playing snooker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |      2      |     3      |      4      |
| Pet   | lizard | hedgehog | cat    | chinchilla |
| Game   | scrabble   | snooker  | whist | chess     |

