.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-17::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: taxi, van, bus, quad-bike
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: climbing, skateboarding, parkour, handball
1. the person driving the bus is on the left of the person driving the taxi##1
2. the person driving the bus is in an even position##4
3. the person who's sport is skateboarding is the person driving the bus##1
4. the person who's sport is parkour is on the left or right of the person who's sport is skateboarding##3
5. the person who's sport is skateboarding is between the person who's sport is handball and the person who's sport is parkour##2
6. the person driving the van is on the right of the person who's sport is handball##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |      3      |    4     |
| Transport         | quad-bike   | bus | taxi | van    |
| Sport   | parkour | skateboarding  | handball     | climbing |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-18::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: folk, electronic, trance, indie
City: berlin, london, hannover, san-francisco
1. the person traveling to london is on the far left##1
2. the fan of trance is on the left or right of the fan of folk##3
3. the fan of indie is on the far left or far right##3
4. the person traveling to hannover is on the left of the person traveling to san-francisco##1
5. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the right of the fan of folk##1
6. the person traveling to hannover is in an even position##4
7. the person traveling to berlin is the fan of electronic##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |   2    |     3      |   4   |
| Music-Genre   | indie | folk    | trance       | electronic |
| City       | london  | hannover | san-francisco | berlin  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-19::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: blue, green, red, pink
House: townhouse, cape-cod, gothic-revival, palace
1. the person who likes blue is on the left of the person who likes pink##1
2. the gothic-revival house is on the left or right of the townhouse house##3
3. the townhouse house is on the left of the gothic-revival house##1
4. the cape-cod house is on the right of the person who likes red##1
5. the person who likes blue is on the right of the gothic-revival house##1
6. the townhouse house is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |     3     |     4     |
| Color   | green | red | blue  | pink |
| House     | townhouse      | gothic-revival       | cape-cod | palace     |

