.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-20::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, soy-milk, tea, hot-chocolate
4 different pets are kept: fish, bird, goldfish, dog
1. the person drinking soy-milk is in an even position##4
2. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left or right of the owner of the fish##3
3. the owner of the bird is between the person drinking almond-milk and the owner of the fish##2
4. the person drinking soy-milk is on the far left or far right##3
5. the owner of the goldfish is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
6. the owner of the goldfish is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |    2    |         3          |    4    |
| Beverage         | almond-milk | tea   | hot-chocolate | soy-milk |
| Pet   | dog          | bird | fish         | goldfish  |

 